                        <p>What are the Cartesian coordinates for the point representing the year <var name="$year"/>? <var name="$point" width="10" /></p>
                        <p>Between <var name="$year"/> and <var name="$next"/>, the wolf population grew by <var name="$change" width="2" /> wolves.</p>
                        <p>List at least three ordered pairs in the graph.</p>
                        <instruction>(Use commas to separate the ordered pairs.)</instruction>
                        <p><var name="$list" evaluator="$listeval" width="30" /></p>
                    </statement>
                </webwork>
            </exercise>
